headline: Third and Grove Acquires Elva, A Shopify Platinum Partner
summary: Third and Grove, a full-service ecommerce and digital practice, today announces its acquisition of Elva, a digital agency recognized for its award-winning branded commerce experiences. As a Shopify Platinum Partner, the combined agency will offer clients access to the highest level of support, tools, and strategic guidance available.
